抗疫一线 | 华润武钢总医院80后护士余芳：“我们自己是很无畏的”。
Yu Fang, a nurse at China Resources Wugang General Hospital 80, says: "We are fearless ourselves."
王雅洁2020-02-06 19:20。
Wang Yajie 2020-02-06 19: 20.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 王雅洁 非典袭来的时候，余芳正值高考。
The economic observation network reporter Wang Yajie SARS attack, Yu Fang was in college entrance examination.
。
.
多年后，新型冠状病毒病毒冲击武汉时，余芳的身份发生了转变。
Years later, when the new coronavirus hit Wuhan, Yufang's identity changed.
。
.
她成为了华润武钢总医院内分泌科护士长，成为了一名披甲陷阵于疫情一线的医护人员。
She became the head nurse of the endocrinology department of China Resources Wugang General Hospital and became a medical worker trapped in the front line of the epidemic.
。
.
2020年2月5日晚间，余芳接受了经济观察网记者的微信电话采访。
On the night of Feb. 5, 2020, Yu Fang gave a microphone interview with a reporter from the Economic Watch network.
。
.
经济观察网：今天是2020年2月5号，往前推，您是几号进入武汉市九医院抗疫前线的？。
Economic Observation Network: Today is February 5, 2020, push forward, what number are you entering Wuhan City Jiu Hospital anti-epidemic front?
余芳：大概在1月24、25号左右进入武汉市九医院开始支援工作。
Yu Fang: About January 24, 25 into Wuhan City about the ninth hospital began to support the work.
我们是三班倒，我现在上白班比较多，是从下午2点到晚上9点的班，主要负责给病患配药、注射、打针，做一些基本的治疗，还有他们的三餐饭需要送，大概就是这些内容。
We work three shifts. I work more day shifts, from 2pm to 9pm, dispensing medication, injections, injections, basic treatment, and their meals.
。
.
经济观察网：这是您第一次参与传染病支援？。
Economic Observation Network: Is this your first time to participate in infectious disease support?
余芳：对，是的。
Yufang: Yes, yes.
。
.
经济观察网：到九医院之后，比较难受，甚至崩溃的时刻出现在何时？因为什么事情？。
Economic Observation Network: After nine hospitals, more uncomfortable, even when the moment of collapse? Because of what?
余芳：最初到这里，武汉市九医院才刚开始被列为定点医院，流程和区域还没有划分得特别清楚，那个时候防护也不到位，心里面很恐慌。
Yufang: When I first arrived here, Wuhan Jiu Hospital was just beginning to be listed as a designated hospital. The process and area were not clearly defined.
但是我们还是勇敢地给病人做治疗，我们的原单位医院提供了很多帮助，还和九医院沟通。
But we bravely treated the patients, our former unit hospital provided a lot of help, and nine hospitals and communication.
。
.
等到九医院基本流程理顺，防护物资逐渐充足后，情况就好起来了。
By the time the basic process of Jiu hospital is straightened out and the protective materials are gradually adequate, the situation will be better.
。
.
只是有时候一些战友们的家里出现了病例，现在病人不是特别多嘛，会出现战友们的家人也被感染的情况，在这种情况下，我们还要工作，这时候心态就会崩掉。
But sometimes there are cases in the homes of our comrades-in-arms, and now there are not too many of them. There are cases where the families of our comrades-in-arms are also infected.
。
.
经济观察网：您抵达九院后，哪些场景给您留下深刻印象，甚至带来冲击？。
Economic Observation Network: When you arrive at the ninth courtyard, which scene impressed you, even brought the impact?
余芳：场景就是我们的同事，在接到他们家人打过来电话的时候。
Yufang: The scene was our colleague, when they got a call from their family.
。
.
就是大家告知家里人，我现在在一线后，会有很多亲朋好友打过来电话问，那时候每个人脸上都是挂着泪的。
That is, we told the family, I am now in the first line, there will be a lot of friends and relatives called to ask, when everyone's face is hung with tears.
。
.
那一幕让人看着特别心酸，我们自己是很无畏的，想着要去照顾病患，但是想到家里面人对自己的担心，可能每个人都会触动自己内心深处的那根弦，都会流眼泪，但是转过头来，擦干眼泪，还是一样到病房里面给病人做各种治疗。
It was a particularly poignant scene, where we were fearless and wanted to take care of the sick, but thinking about the worries of people at home might cause everyone to touch the chord in their hearts and shed tears, but turn around and dry the tears, or go to the ward to do all kinds of treatment.
。
.
经济观察网：家人对您工作的态度是怎样的？。
Economic Watch: What is the attitude of your family towards your work?
余芳：家里是湖北人，但不是武汉的，很早之前我就把他们送回老家去了，我这次出来支援前线，考虑了很久才告诉他们，不过我也没有说得特别严重，只是说我到外面的医院帮忙去了。
Yufang: My family is from Hubei, but not Wuhan. I sent them back to my hometown a long time ago. I went out to support them and thought about it for a long time.
。
.
看到这次疫情，我就想到很多年前非典的时候，我正好高中毕业，那个时候我觉得医护人员非常伟大，保护了我们整个国家，我非常敬仰，于是所有的志愿都填报了护理专业，走上了这个岗位。
Seeing this outbreak, I think of the SARS years ago, when I graduated from high school, when I thought the medical staff was great and protected our country. I was so respected that all the volunteers entered the nursing profession and took up this position.
。
.
这一次需要医护人员来支援，我也赶紧报名了。
I needed medical support this time, and I signed up quickly.
。
.
经济观察网：现在还恐惧吗？。
Economic Watch: Are you still afraid?
余芳：面对这次的疫情，每个人心里都有恐惧，但我不会说太多，更不会和家人讲太多，我毕竟是医护人员，要战胜自己的内心恐惧。
Yu Fang: In the face of this epidemic, everyone has fear, but I will not say too much, not to mention too much with their families, I am a medical staff, to overcome their fear.
我们如果表现出来被吓到，病患也会受影响，从职业的角度说，我们首先需要保证病患的稳定和安全。
If we show that we are frightened, the patient will be affected. From a professional point of view, we need to ensure the stability and security of the patient first.
。
.
经济观察网：下班之后呢？又要如何消化自己的情绪？。
Economic Observation Network: What happens after work? How do you digest your emotions?
余芳：我们休息的时候，会岔开一下话题，聊下天，更多的是同事们一起聊天和想念自己的家人，不好的情绪在平常的说说笑笑中就消失了。
Yufang: When we relax, we will deviate from the topic and talk about the next day. More often than not, colleagues talk and miss their families.
。
.
和病人在一起时，也会给我们带来一些信心。
Being with patients also gives us some confidence.
。
.
我们刚到九医院的时候，曾经有一个病患家属问我们从哪里来，我们说从外面过来支援的，他又问我们是哪家医院的，我们告诉他是华润武钢总医院，他当时做了一个动作，双手作揖，给我们拜了几下，我当时就觉得心情非常激动的感觉。
When we first arrived at the Nine Hospitals, we were asked by a patient's family where we came from, we said we had support from outside, and he asked which hospital we were from. We told him it was China Resources Wugang General Hospital.
。
.
病人们很感谢有人去帮他们，我们也从病人那里得到缓解，互相帮助吧。
The patients are very grateful to someone to help them, we also get relief from the patients, help each other.
。
.
经济观察网：实际工作中遇到过哪些困难？需要什么支持？。
Economic Observation Network: What difficulties have you encountered in your practical work? What support do you need?
余芳：主要是物资方面的困难，如果物资不充足，我们医护人员的安全就得不到保证，其实相比于疫情来说，我们并不是特别恐惧。
Yufang: It is mainly material difficulties. If we do not have enough supplies, the safety of our medical staff will not be guaranteed.
我们恐惧的，是防护不到位，防护物资不够，毕竟我们每天都需要面对每一位病人，多少会有点恐惧的，只要能让我们防护做到位，恐惧便会减少很多。
What we fear is inadequate protection, inadequate supplies, after all, we have to face every patient every day, a little bit of fear, as long as we can protect ourselves a bit, fear will be much less.
。
.
经济观察网：等到疫情结束后，最想做的事情是什么？。
Economic Watch: What is the most desirable thing to do when the epidemic is over?
余芳：最想做的事情可能就是隔离14天之后，如果没有出现任何症状，我就去见自己的家人。
Yufang: The thing I would like to do most of all is to stay in isolation for 14 days and see my family if there are no symptoms.
我要好好地拥抱他们。
I'm gonna give them a big hug.
。
.
